&lt;p&gt;1. Donald Olander, &amp;quot;Fundamental Aspects of Nuclear Reactor Fuel Elements&amp;quot;, 1976, Technical Information Center, Energy Research and Development Administration.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2. Robert Cochran and Nicholas Tsoulfanidis, &amp;quot;The Nuclear Fuel Cycle: Analysis and Management&amp;quot;, 2nd Edition, ANS, La Grange Park, Illinois, USA, 1999.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3. Nicholas Tsoulfanidis, &amp;ldquo;The Nuclear Fuel Cycle&amp;rdquo;, ANS, La Grange Park, Illinois, USA, 2013.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4. Neil Todreas and Mujid Kazimi, &amp;quot;Nuclear Systems I&amp;quot;, 2nd Edition, CRC Press, 2012.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5. Brian Frost, &amp;ldquo;Nuclear Fuel Elements &amp;ndash; Design, Fabrication and Performance&amp;rdquo;, Pergamon Press, 1982.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Grading:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
