Quizzes (10%)&lt;br /&gt;
Two Exams (40%)&lt;br /&gt;
Project (20%)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The computer code projects will utilize the NRC fuel performance codes - FRAPCON (steady state and depletion) and FRAPTRAN (transient) analysis of LWR fuel designs in order to illustrate important fuel modeling concepts discussed in class.&lt;/p&gt;
